avyweight titles}}\n|-\n|22\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|22\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Joey Abell]]\n|TKO\n|4 (10), {{small|1:48}}\n|15 Feb 2014\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Copper Box Arena]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|21\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|21\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Steve Cunningham]]\n|KO\n|7 (12), {{small|2:55}}\n|20 Apr 2013\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[The Theater at Madison Square Garden]], [[New York City, New York]], US}}\n|\n|-\n|20\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|20\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Kevin Johnson (boxer)|Kevin Johnson]]\n|UD\n|12\n|1 Dec 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Odyssey Arena, Belfast, Northern Ireland}}\n|\n|-\n|19\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|19\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Vinny Maddalone]]\n|TKO\n|5 (12), {{small|1:35}}\n|7 Jul 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Hand Arena, [[Clevedon]], England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won vacant [[World Boxing Organization|WBO]] Inter-Continental heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|18\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|18\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Martin Rogan]]\n|TKO\n|5 (12), {{small|3:00}}\n|14 Apr 2012\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Odyssey Arena]], [[Belfast]], Northern Ireland}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won vacant [[Boxing Union of Ireland#Heavyweight|Irish heavyweight title]]}}\n|-\n|17\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|17\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Neven Pajkic]]\n|TKO\n|3 (12), {{small|2:44}}\n|12 Nov 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[EventCity]], [[Manchester]], England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained Commonwealth heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|16\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|16\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Nicolai Firtha\n|TKO\n|5 (12), {{small|2:19}}\n|18 Sep 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[King's Hall, Belfast|King's Hall]], [[Belfast]], Northern Ireland}}\n|\n|-\n|15\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|15\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Dereck Chisora]]\n|UD\n|12\n|23 Jul 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Wembley Arena, London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won [[list of British heavyweight boxing champions|British]] and [[list of Commonwealth Boxing Council champions#Heavyweight|Commonwealth heavyweight titles]]}}\n|-\n|14\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|14\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|BRA}} Marcelo Luiz Nascimento\n|KO\n|5 (10), {{small|2:48}}\n|19 Feb 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Wembley Arena]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|13\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|13\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Zack Page\n|{{abbr|UD|Unanimous decision}}\n|8\n|[[Jean Pascal vs. Bernard Hopkins|19 Dec 2010]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|CAN}} {{small|[[Colis\u00e9e Pepsi]], [[Quebec City, Quebec]], Canada}}\n|\n|-\n|12\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|12\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Rich Power\n|PTS\n|8\n|10 Sep 2010\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|11\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|11\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[John McDermott (boxer)|John McDermott]]\n|TKO\n|9 (12), {{small|1:08}}\n|25 Jun 2010\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Brentwood Centre Arena, Brentwood, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won vacant English heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|10\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|10\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} Hans-Joerg Blasko\n|TKO\n|1 (8), {{small|2:14}}\n|5 Mar 2010\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Leisure Centre, [[Huddersfield]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|9\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|9\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|CZE}} Tomas Mrazek\n|PTS\n|6\n|26 Sep 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|IRE}} {{small|[[The O2 (Dublin)|The O2]], [[Dublin]], Ireland}}\n|\n|-\n|8\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|8\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[John McDermott (boxer)|John McDermott]]\n|{{abbr|PTS|Points decision}}\n|10\n|11 Sep 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Brentwood Centre Arena]], [[Brentwood, Essex|Brentwood]], England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won [[British Boxing Board of Control#Councils|English heavyweight title]]}}\n|-\n|7\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|7\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|LAT}} Aleksandrs Selezens\n|TKO\n|3 (6), {{small|0:48}}\n|18 Jul 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|6\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|6\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Scott Belshaw]]\n|TKO\n|2 (8), {{small|0:52}}\n|23 May 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Watford Colosseum|Colosseum]], [[Watford]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|5\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|5\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} Matthew Ellis\n|{{abbr|KO|Knockout}}\n|1 (6), {{small|0:48}}\n|11 Apr 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[York Hall]], [[London]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|4\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|4\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Lee Swaby]]\n|TKO\n|4 (6), {{small|3:00}}\n|14 Mar 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Aston Events Centre]], [[Birmingham]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|3\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|3\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|RUS}} Daniil Peretyatko\n|TKO\n|2 (6), {{small|3:00}}\n|28 Feb 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Showground, [[Norwich]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|2\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|2\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Marcel Zeller]]\n|TKO\n|3 (6), {{small|2:50}}\n|17 Jan 2009\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[DW Stadium]], [[Wigan]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|1\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|1\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|HUN}} B\u00e9la Gy\u00f6ngy\u00f6si\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|1 (6), {{small|2:14}}\n|[[Carl Froch vs. Jean Pascal|6 Dec 2008]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[National Ice Centre]], [[Nottingham]], England}}\n|\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Div col}}\n* [[List of world heavyweight boxing champions]]\n* [[List of WBA world champions]]\n* [[List of IBF world champions]]\n* [[List of WBO world champions]]\n* [[List of IBO world champions]]\n* [[List of The Ring world champions|List of ''The Ring'' world champions]]\n* [[List of European Boxing Union heavyweight champions]]\n* [[List of British heavyweight boxing champions]]\n* [[List of Commonwealth Boxing Council champions]]\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*{{Official website|http://www.mrtysonfury.com/}}\n*{{Boxrec|id=479205}}\n\n{{s-start-collapsible|header={{s-sports}} }}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Amateur boxing titles}}\n{{s-before|before=[[David Price (boxer)|David Price]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of ABA super-heavyweight champions|ABA super-heavyweight champion]]\n|years=2008}}\n{{s-after|after=[[Simon Vallily]]}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Regional boxing titles}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[John McDermott (boxer)|John McDermott]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[British Boxing Board of Control|English]] [[heavyweight]] champion\n|years=11 September 2009 \u2013 March 2010<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=Himself}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=Himself}}\n{{s-ttl|title=English heavyweight champion\n|years=25 June 2010 \u2013 July 2011<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|rows=3|next=David Price}}\n{{s-bef|rows=2|before=[[Dereck Chisora]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of British heavyweight boxing champions|British heavyweight champion]]\n|years=23 July 2011 \u2013 8 February 2012<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of Commonwealth Boxing Council champions#Heavyweight|Commonwealth heavyweight champion]]\n|years=23 July 2011 \u2013 8 February 2012<br>Vacated}}\n{{